# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:30
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_26c8bd29:

    # gg "Man, I haven't gone go-karting in a LONG time!"
    gg "Caramba, já não ando de kart há MUITO tempo!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:31
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_425c7596:

    # gg "I'm looking forward to this."
    gg "Estou ansioso por isto."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:32
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_c3947180:

    # "While we wait for our turn to drive, we have some time to chat."
    "Enquanto esperamos pela nossa vez de conduzir, temos algum tempo para conversar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:40
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_dba2e530:

    # "Finally, it's our turn."
    "Finalmente, é a nossa vez."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:46
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_8f9b8839:

    # "We line up and get ready to take off."
    "Alinhamos e preparamo-nos para arrancar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:48
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_18ef0fb8:

    # gg "Hope you're ready to eat my dust."
    gg "Espero que estejas pronta para comer o meu pó."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:49
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_53dbc1f5:

    # pc "Yeah right. You're going down."
    pc "Pois, claro. Vais perder."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:50
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_800a9087:

    # gg "No, you!"
    gg "Não, tu!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:57
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_26aa19ac:

    # "When the light comes on and the buzzer sounds, she pulls in front very quickly. My kart is not accelerating as fast as hers, no matter how much I mash on the gas."
    "Quando a luz acende e o alarme soa, ela passa para a frente muito rapidamente. O meu kart não acelera tão rápido quanto o dela, por mais que eu carregue no acelerador."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:64
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_1ec15e0c:

    # "As much as I try to catch up, she's just too fast. She takes the corners perfectly, barely letting off the accelerator."
    "Por mais que eu tente alcançá-la, ela é simplesmente demasiado rápida. Ela faz as curvas na perfeição, mal tirando o pé do acelerador."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:70
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_d3f8613e:

    # "By the end of our time, she is well in the lead, leaving me far behind."
    "No final do nosso tempo, ela está bem na liderança, deixando-me muito para trás."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:77
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_855b783c:

    # "But once I'm able to get the kart up to top speed, I start catching up with her."
    "Mas assim que consigo levar o kart à velocidade máxima, começo a alcançá-la."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:83
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_349acc4b:

    # "Then, on the final lap, I'm barely able to slip past her just before we cross the finish line."
    "Então, na última volta, consigo ultrapassá-la por pouco mesmo antes de cruzarmos a linha de chegada."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:87
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_96accbe9:

    # gg "That was fun!"
    gg "Foi divertido!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:89
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_3f94ba4d:

    # pc "Yeah it was. You kicked my ass."
    pc "Sim, foi. Deste-me uma coça."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:90
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_1a12d8de:

    # gg "Lots of Mario Kart practice."
    gg "Muita prática no Mario Kart."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:92
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_45c6ecca:

    # gg "I can't believe you caught up to me!"
    gg "Não acredito que me alcançaste!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:93
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_778b032e:

    # gg "You're a damn good driver!"
    gg "És uma piloto fantástica!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:94
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_c6880d17:

    # pc "Thanks!"
    pc "Obrigada!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianDates/adriangokartdate.rpy:97
translate portuguese adriangokartstartdate_9f35c8f5:

    # "When we're ready, I drive her home and walk her up to her front door."
    "Quando estamos prontos, levo-a a casa e acompanho-a até à porta de entrada."

